{"type":null,"faqId":37092,"title":"手环是否可以显示来电姓名？为什么有的显示姓名，有的显示号码？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\r\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<div class=\"detail_c_1 fl mt1\">\n<div style=\"POSITION: relative; PADDING-LEFT: 5%; PADDING-RIGHT: 5%\" id=\"softwareDescription\" class=\"column fl\" jQuery17105618356093124175=\"16\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>、手环支持姓名推送功能。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">如果不能推送，可能是因为不小心拒绝了电话本的访问权限，可以这么操作：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">确认手机型号及手机系统，<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）华为手机且手机系统是<span lang=\"EN-US\">EMUI4.0</span>：请用户打开蓝牙列表，点击华为<span lang=\"EN-US\">B2</span>—<span lang=\"EN-US\">XXX</span>后面的叹号，进入设置界面，打开共享联系人即可，如果还是无法推送姓名，请上升<span lang=\"EN-US\">CSE</span>处理；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）非华为<span lang=\"EN-US\">EMUI4.0</span>手机：每次手机连接上手环后，手机会提示“电话簿权限申请”提示框，点击是允许手环访问手机上的电话本即可。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">如果不小心点击了拒绝访问，可以将蓝牙设备删除，重启手环进行蓝牙配对。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>、为什么有的显示姓名，有的显示号码？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）手环和手机建立蓝牙连接；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）蓝牙连接要获取手机联系人的权限。如果第一次没有选择读取权限，取消配对后重新配对获取手机联系人的权限；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>）手机电话本中存储了有包含关系或者相同的姓名时无法推送姓名的问题，目前<span lang=\"EN-US\">USB</span>固件升级<span lang=\"EN-US\">Beta</span>版本<span lang=\"EN-US\">21.10.07.05.00</span>及其之后的版本已经优化并在花粉论坛发布；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）来电推送功能依托于手机推送，部分手机不能推送存储在<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡中的用户姓名（例如：三星不支持）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n</div>\n<!--\n<div id=\"floatDiv\"></div>\n--></div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2256","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750142000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":202,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,来电显,姓名,姓名推送,联系人","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}